Object.Field: CASE WHEN AGGREGATE2.COUPON_AMOUNT > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END

CASE WHEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_UNIT = 'Curency' THEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE WHEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_UNIT = 'Percentage' THEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE * AGGREGATE.SUBTOTAL / 100 WHEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_UNIT = 'Auto' AND STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE > 100 THEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE WHEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_UNIT = 'Auto' AND STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE < 1 THEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE * AGGREGATE.SUBTOTAL WHEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_UNIT = 'Auto' AND STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE >= 1 AND STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE <= 100 THEN STG_CHANNEL.FEE_VALUE * AGGREGATE.SUBTOTAL / 100 ELSE 0 END

CASE WHEN STG_COUPON.COUPON_TYPE = 'Currency' THEN STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE WHEN STG_COUPON.COUPON_TYPE = 'Percentage' THEN AGGREGATE.SUBTOTAL * STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE / 100 WHEN STG_COUPON.COUPON_TYPE = 'Auto' AND STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE > 100 THEN STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE WHEN STG_COUPON.COUPON_TYPE = 'Auto' AND STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE < 1 THEN AGGREGATE.SUBTOTAL * STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE WHEN STG_COUPON.COUPON_TYPE = 'Auto' AND STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE >= 1 AND STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE <= 100 THEN AGGREGATE.SUBTOTAL * STG_COUPON.COUPON_VALUE / 100 ELSE 0 END

CASE WHEN AGGREGATE1.SUBTOTAL >= AGGREGATE1.BILL_MIN_AMOUNT AND AGGREGATE1.COUPON_AMOUNT > AGGREGATE1.MAX_DISCOUNT THEN AGGREGATE1.MAX_DISCOUNT WHEN AGGREGATE1.SUBTOTAL >= AGGREGATE1.BILL_MIN_AMOUNT AND AGGREGATE1.COUPON_AMOUNT <= AGGREGATE1.MAX_DISCOUNT THEN AGGREGATE1.COUPON_AMOUNT ELSE 0 END
